''This is an anti-aircraft autocannon introduced by the British Vickers Ltd. company. <br>Also known as the "pom-pom" gun due to its firing sound and it's two round burst, it was licensed but also produced domestically. It was gradually replaced by more modern anti-aircraft guns.''

